Both of the Slaver Enforcers must be killed first!
Slaver Guardfemale1
\n<Female Slaver Guard>I'm so glad that our families
are free! In return for your service to us, I'll promise
to guard this hold for you!
Slaver Guard2_face
\n<Male Slaver Guard>Thank you so much....
Slaver Guardfemale1
\n<Female Slaver Guard>All of the guards will serve you.
\!We were once slaves ourselves but they trained some
of us to fight and do their bidding. Most of the others
weren't so lucky....
Slaver Guard2_face
\n<Male Slaver Guard>I was just a boy when they took me
from my mother...\!I was trained then sold to various
fighting pits. After years of killing, they sold me back
here to be a guard. \!Then you came.
Slaver Guardfemale1
\n<Female Slaver Guard>We will keep this hold well
guarded!
Slaver Guard1_face
\n<Male Slaver Guard>You are a hero among us.
Slaver Guard2_face
\n<Male Slaver Guard>I will stay and serve you.
Slaver Guardfemale2
\n<Female Slaver Guard>If you ever need me for anything,
just ask!
Slaver Guardfemale2
\n<Female Slaver Guard>If you ever need me for anything,
just ask!
Slaver Guard2_face
\n<Male Slaver Guard>I'll kill any Slaver I see....
Slaver Guard1_face
\n<Male Slaver Guard>Is there anything that I can do for you?
Slaver Guard2_face
\n<Male Slaver Guard>The vault is just behind me.
